#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:159
msgid ""
"In the Dashboards app, go to :menuselection:`Configuration --> Dashboards`."
msgstr ""
"Siirry Koontin­äytöt-sovelluksessa kohtaan :menuselection:`Asetukset --> "
