"kirjautua `Axivoxin hallintakonsoliin <https://manage.axivox.com>`_ ja "
"yhdistää dynaamisia agentteja jonoon manuaalisesti."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/axivox/call_queues.rst:70
msgid ""
"To connect an agent, click :guilabel:`Queues`, located in the left-hand "
"menu. Doing so opens the :guilabel:`Queues` dashboard, with a few different "
